Petrominerales to List Shares in Colombia Within One Month

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-05-12T21:58:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/petrominerales-to-list-shares-in-colombia-within-one-month.html
Petrominerales Ltd. (PMG)  expects to list
its shares on  Colombia ’s bourse in as soon as one month, said
Tannya Morales, Vice-President of Finance for the company.  “We should list in the next month,” Morales said in a
phone interview from Bogota, “It makes sense from a strategic
point of view with our operations in  Peru  and Colombia and the
integration of exchanges between Colombia, Peru and  Chile .”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
 bschmidt16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  